@startuml

StateMachine VideoSuggestionSystem
  state UserRequestReceived
  state GatheringVideos
  state AddingDetails
  state SendingVideos

  [*]->UserRequestReceived: ReceiveVideoSuggestionRequest

  UserRequestReceived --> GatheringVideos: OnUserProfileOrPreferences
  UserRequestReceived --> GatheringVideos: OnTrendingVideosFromArea
  UserRequestReceived --> GatheringVideos: OnSimilarTaggedVideos
  UserRequestReceived --> GatheringVideos: OnSimilarGenreVideos
  UserRequestReceived --> GatheringVideos: OnPromotedVideos

  GatheringVideos --> AddingDetails: OnGatheredVideos

  AddingDetails --> SendingVideos: OnAddedThumbnailsAndViewCounts

  SendingVideos --> UserRequestReceived: OnSuggestedVideosSent

@enduml
